Elasticsearch + delete-by-query (https://download.elasticsearch.org/elasticsearch/release/org/elasticsearch/distribution/tar/elasticsearch/2.1.1/elasticsearch-2.1.1.tar.gz, bin/plugin install delete-by-query)
(d3)
(require.js)
(Python 2.7)
hamlib (https://github.com/N0NB/hamlib, bindings patch, python-dev, autoconf, libtool, swig, texinfo)

  git clone https://github.com/N0NB/hamlib
  cd hamlib
  git apply [bindings patch]
  cd ..
  mkdir hamlib-build; cd hamlib-build
  sh ../hamlib/autogen.sh CFLAGS="-g -O0" --with-python-binding --without-cxx-binding
  make
  sudo make install
  sudo ldconfig

piSpecMon/spectrum$ ./create.sh
create users.passwords

disable console on serial port using  $sudo raspi-config
dmesg | grep tty for diagnostics

elasticsearch$ bin/elasticsearch
python server.py
